Name: Electrify America Charging Station
Reviews: ['Wilson Lin: Every time, at least 1 or 2 out of 4 chargers is always broken and out of service. And the two that are working, it’s charging at 40kwh rather than 150. It’s been like this for a couple of months as of writing this. If you really need charging last minute, just go to another station instead of wasting time getting here since very likely the other two chargers are almost always occupied even at midnight. 😅 also, the card readers on any of these never work, install the app on your phone prior to charging.', 'Shirin Gallagher: All chargers up and running when I was here; check plug share for more up to date info than what you will find on Google.', 'Stella Z: Worst experience. Out of 4 station, 3 have both chords cut off. The only one left has two plugs but is not shareable. A total mess', 'Peter N: Great to see EV charging at U Village.
